# Proxy all list share links to the backend.
# The backend's renderSharedListPage() queries Supabase with the admin client
# (already configured in Render) — no Netlify env vars required.
#
# /shared/:token  — legacy format; kept for old links / QR codes
# /s/:username/:token — pretty format generated by the mobile app
/shared/*  https://qulture-backend-api.onrender.com/shared/:splat  200
/s/*       https://qulture-backend-api.onrender.com/s/:splat       200

/shared-plan/*   /shared-plan/index.html   200

# Proxy personalized taste snapshot links to the backend.
# URL format: qulture.app/q/{firstName}s-qulture  (e.g. qulture.app/q/cedrics-qulture)
/q/*  https://qulture-backend-api.onrender.com/q/:splat  200
